N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 91.19 - Court procedure for uniform traffic ticket (tsleandd area)

State Regulations

When a traffic violation matter, for which a uniform
traffic ticket has been issued, has been disposed of, the court shall complete
parts I and II of the uniform traffic ticket. Part I should be retained by the
court, and may be used as the court's docket. Part II should be forwarded by
the court to its assigned data entry location, in the manner prescribed by the
commissioner. Notes
